   "source": [
    "This is the equivalent of **'Quick delivery, everything packaged well, items as described! Thank you'**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "74936a1f-9ff3-41ca-90ec-2ade9a087100",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Now, each sentence will not be of the same length. So, we pad each sentence with 0 index so that each sentence becomes of equal length.\n",
    "\n",
    "Before that, we would need the length of longest sentence."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 20,
   "id": "257d9d49-c950-42a8-89a3-f5feefca6460",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "review_lengths=[]\n",
    "\n",
    "for review in int_encoded_X_train:\n",
    "    review_length = len(review)\n",
    "    review_lengths.append(review_length)"
   ]
  },
